628
00:28:27,800 --> 00:28:29,399
I MEAN THREE HOURS.

629
00:28:29,466 --> 00:28:31,432
YOU LISTEN TO ME, MERLE.

630
00:28:31,500 --> 00:28:36,765
<i>PASADO UNO PARA EL OFICIAL
DE IMIGRACIóN, ¿EH?</i>

