633
00:28:48,000 --> 00:28:49,832
<i>CERTAMENTE, SIGNORE. </i>

634
00:28:49,900 --> 00:28:51,432
<i>CERTAMENTE. </i>

635
00:28:51,500 --> 00:28:54,999
<i>IL TRADIRE DIECI
